# My portfolio

![alt text] (https://scontent-b-sjc.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/t1.0-9/10362859_10152162660885748_4717347878838163006_n.jpg)

My name is [Alex Corey](http://twitter.com/acoreynews) and here's some of my work:

* [Writing Old Central Library's Next Chapter](http://voiceofsandiego.org/2013/07/17/writing-old-central-librarys-next-chapter/)  - A story that I wrote for Voice of San Diego.

* [San Diego's Top Talking Head](http://voiceofsandiego.org/2013/07/29/san-diegos-top-talking-head/) - A profile that I wrote for Voice of San Diego.

* [Fact Check: A 'Redundant' Homeless Shelter] (http://voiceofsandiego.org/2013/07/24/fact-check-a-redundant-homeless-shelter/) - A small data story (and Fact Check) that I did for Voice of San Diego.

* [Un Domingo con #Reforma150] (http://www.elnuevosol.net/noticias/un-domingo-con-los-reforma150) - A news story that I wrote for El Nuevo Sol about immigration protests at the San Diego/Tijuana border.

* [Tres historias del tercer ’round’ de los que quieren regresar a casa] (http://www.elnuevosol.net/reportajes/tres-historias-del-tercer-round-de-los-que-quieren-regresar-a-casa) - Another news story that I wrote for El Nuevo Sol about immigration protests at the San Diego/Tijuana border.
